HEADWORD: Mythological
<hw>Myth`o*log"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>mythologicus</ets>:
cf. F. <ets>mytholigique</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of or pertaining
to mythology or to myths; <as>as, <ex>mythological</ex>
creatures</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Myth`o*log"ic*al*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
