<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>based on or told of in traditional stories; lacking
factual basis or historical validity; mythical; fabulous.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> fabulous, mythic, mythical.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

